headline: Consumer Discretionary: How Tesla led the sector's gains in 2024
summary: The Consumer Discretionary Select Sector SPDR Fund (XLY) has surged approximately 30% in 2024, with Tesla (TSLA) emerging as the sector's leading performer. Yahoo Finance Special Reporter Akiko Fujita examines the key factors behind this impressive performance. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Morning Brief here. This post was written by Angel Smith
